the journey ( &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2014 malaysian chinese film directed by chiu keng guan and written by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; lee . the film is known for being the highest grossing malaysian film in 2014 . the journey won several awards in 27th malaysian film festival for the best &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; language local film , best cinematography and best actor , leading actor frankie lee being the oldest winner for that particular category .